Title: Bridging the Dimensional Gap

Domain Wall in Three DimensionsAuthors: H. Arod\'z

Comments: 14 pages, Latex 2.09, no figures. Presented at XXXVIII Cracow School

of Theoretical Physics, Zakopane, 1-10 June 1998Journal-ref: Acta Phys.Polon. B29 (1998) 3725-3737

Improved expansion in width is applied to a curved domain wall innonrelativistic dissipative $\lambda(\Phi^2 - v^2)^2 $ model with real scalarorder parameter $\Phi$. Approximate analytic description of such a domain wallto second order in the width is presented.